und</li>\n<li>Game has only one level</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>What went well</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Alpha designed the UI.</li>\n<li>Alpha tested the game and liked it.</li>\n<li>Titan spent several hours learning how to make models with Blender. He managed to come up with textures and models for this game.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>What needs to change</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Put more thought into the game ideas </li>\n<li>Make games with longer play time</li>\n<li>Spend more time working on the games</li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"week_two"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216","440568431"]}